"use client" import { useState, useEffect } from "react" import * as XLSX from "xlsx" const Logs = () => { const [logs, setLogs] = useState([]) const [filteredLogs, setFilteredLogs] = useState([]) const [branches, setBranches] = useState([]) const [materialData, setMaterialData] = useState([]) const [filteredMaterialData, setFilteredMaterialData] = useState([]) const [filters, setFilters] = useState({ dateFrom: "", dateTo: "", branch: "All", user: "", module: "All", action: "All", }) const [materialFilters, setMaterialFilters] = useState({ dateFrom: "", dateTo: "", partyName: "", grade: "All", }) const modules = [ "Employee Management", "Branch Management", "Project Management", "Role Management", "Vehicle Entry", "Supplier Details", "PO Details", "GRN Management", "System", ] const actions = ["Add", "Update", "Delete", "Inaction", "Login", "Logout", "View", "Export"] const grades = ["M20", "M25", "M30", "M35", "M40", "M45", "M50"] useEffect(() => { // Load logs and branches from localStorage const savedLogs = localStorage.getItem("systemLogs") const savedBranches = localStorage.getItem("branches") const savedMaterialData = localStorage.getItem("materialData") if (savedLogs) { const logData = JSON.parse(savedLogs) setLogs(logData) setFilteredLogs(logData) } else { // Generate sample logs for demonstration generateSampleLogs() } if (savedBranches) { setBranches(JSON.parse(savedBranches)) } if (savedMaterialData) { const materialLogData = JSON.parse(savedMaterialData) setMaterialData(materialLogData) setFilteredMaterialData(materialLogData) } else { // Generate sample material data generateSampleMaterialData() } }, []) const generateSampleLogs = () => { const sampleLogs = [ { id: 1, sno: 1, branchName: "Main Branch", moduleName: "Employee Management", actionPerformed: "Add", actionBy: "admin", actionOn: "John Doe Employee Record", timestamp: new Date(Date.now() - 86400000).toISOString(), ipAddress: "192.168.1.100", }, { id: 2, sno: 2, branchName: "Main Branch", moduleName: "System", actionPerformed: "Login", actionBy: "admin", actionOn: "System Login", timestamp: new Date(Date.now() - 3600000).toISOString(), ipAddress: "192.168.1.100", }, { id: 3, sno: 3, branchName: "Branch A", moduleName: "Vehicle Entry", actionPerformed: "Add", actionBy: "user1", actionOn: "Vehicle Entry Record", timestamp: new Date(Date.now() - 7200000).toISOString(), ipAddress: "192.168.1.101", }, ] setLogs(sampleLogs) setFilteredLogs(sampleLogs) localStorage.setItem("systemLogs", JSON.stringify(sampleLogs)) } const generateSampleMaterialData = () => { const sampleMaterialData = [ { id: 1, sno: 1, date: "2024-01-15", partyName: "ABC Construction", pb: "P", grade: "M25", qty: 50, rate: 4500, billNo: "INV001", billDate: "2024-01-15", cement: 15.5, silo2: 12.3, mm20: 25.8, mm12: 18.2, mSand: 22.5, admixTrue: 0.8, flyAshUsage: 5.2, remark: "Quality approved", }, { id: 2, sno: 2, date: "2024-01-16", partyName: "XYZ Builders", pb: "B", grade: "M30", qty: 75, rate: 4800, billNo: "INV002", billDate: "2024-01-16", cement: 18.2, silo2: 14.5, mm20: 28.5, mm12: 20.8, mSand: 25.2, admixTrue: 1.2, flyAshUsage: 6.8, remark: "Delivered on time", }, { id: 3, sno: 3, date: "2024-01-17", partyName: "PQR Infrastructure", pb: "P", grade: "M20", qty: 40, rate: 4200, billNo: "INV003", billDate: "2024-01-17", cement: 12.8, silo2: 10.2, mm20: 22.5, mm12: 16.8, mSand: 19.5, admixTrue: 0.6, flyAshUsage: 4.2, remark: "Standard mix", }, { id: 4, sno: 4, date: "2024-01-18", partyName: "LMN Contractors", pb: "B", grade: "M35", qty: 60, rate: 5200, billNo: "INV004", billDate: "2024-01-18", cement: 20.5, silo2: 16.8, mm20: 30.2, mm12: 22.5, mSand: 27.8, admixTrue: 1.5, flyAshUsage: 7.5, remark: "High strength mix", }, { id: 5, sno: 5, date: "2024-01-19", partyName: "RST Developers", pb: "P", grade: "M40", qty: 85, rate: 5800, billNo: "INV005", billDate: "2024-01-19", cement: 25.2, silo2: 20.5, mm20: 35.8, mm12: 26.2, mSand: 32.5, admixTrue: 2.0, flyAshUsage: 9.2, remark: "Premium grade", }, ] setMaterialData(sampleMaterialData) setFilteredMaterialData(sampleMaterialData) localStorage.setItem("materialData", JSON.stringify(sampleMaterialData)) } useEffect(() => { let filtered = logs // Filter by date range if (filters.dateFrom) { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => new Date(log.timestamp) >= new Date(filters.dateFrom)) } if (filters.dateTo) { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => new Date(log.timestamp) <= new Date(filters.dateTo + "T23:59:59")) } // Filter by branch if (filters.branch !== "All") { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => log.branchName === filters.branch) } // Filter by user if (filters.user) { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => log.actionBy.toLowerCase().includes(filters.user.toLowerCase())) } // Filter by module if (filters.module !== "All") { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => log.moduleName === filters.module) } // Filter by action if (filters.action !== "All") { filtered = filtered.filter((log) => log.actionPerformed === filters.action) } setFilteredLogs(filtered) }, [logs, filters]) useEffect(() => { let filtered = materialData // Filter by date range if (materialFilters.dateFrom) { filtered = filtered.filter((item) => new Date(item.date) >= new Date(materialFilters.dateFrom)) } if (materialFilters.dateTo) { filtered = filtered.filter((item) => new Date(item.date) <= new Date(materialFilters.dateTo)) } // Filter by party name if (materialFilters.partyName) { filtered = filtered.filter((item) => item.partyName.toLowerCase().includes(materialFilters.partyName.toLowerCase()), ) } // Filter by grade if (materialFilters.grade !== "All") { filtered = filtered.filter((item) => item.grade === materialFilters.grade) } setFilteredMaterialData(filtered) }, [materialData, materialFilters]) const handleFilterChange = (field, value) => { setFilters((prev) => ({ ...prev, [field]: value, })) } const handleMaterialFilterChange = (field, value) => { setMaterialFilters((prev) => ({ ...prev, [field]: value, })) } const clearFilters = () => { setFilters({ dateFrom: "", dateTo: "", branch: "All", user: "", module: "All", action: "All", }) } const clearMaterialFilters = () => { setMaterialFilters({ dateFrom: "", dateTo: "", partyName: "", grade: "All", }) } const exportToExcel = () => { const worksheet = XLSX.utils.json_to_sheet(filteredLogs) const workbook = XLSX.utils.book_new() XLSX.utils.book_append_sheet(workbook, worksheet, "System Logs") XLSX.writeFile(workbook, "system_logs.xlsx") } const exportMaterialToExcel = () => { const worksheet = XLSX.utils.json_to_sheet(filteredMaterialData) const workbook = XLSX.utils.book_new() XLSX.utils.book_append_sheet(workbook, worksheet, "Material Data") XLSX.writeFile(workbook, "material_data.xlsx") } const exportToPDF = () => { const printWindow = window.open("", "_blank") const tableHTML = document.querySelector(".logs-table").outerHTML printWindow.document.write(` System Logs Report

System Logs Report

Generated on: ${new Date().toLocaleDateString()}

Total Records: ${filteredLogs.length}

${tableHTML} `) printWindow.document.close() printWindow.print() } const getActionClass = (action) => { switch (action.toLowerCase()) { case "add": return "action-add" case "update": return "action-update" case "delete": return "action-delete" case "login": return "action-login" case "logout": return "action-logout" default: return "action-default" } } return (
